---

### 10.6 Accessibility Checklist

- ✅ **Label**: Always include `label` prop (or use aria-label)
- ✅ **Required Indicator**: Shows `*` when `required={true}`
- ✅ **Error Association**: Uses `aria-invalid` and `aria-describedby`
- ✅ **Helper Text**: Properly associated with input
- ✅ **Keyboard Navigation**: Tab order maintained
- ✅ **Focus Indicators**: Clear focus ring
- ✅ **Autocomplete**: Supports autocomplete attribute

---

### 10.7 Design Specifications

**Spacing**:
- Height: 48px (py-3 with text-base)
- Padding: px-4 (horizontal), py-3 (vertical)
- Icon padding: pl-11 (left icon), pr-11 (right icon)
- Label margin: mb-2 (8px below label)
- Helper text margin: mt-2 (8px above helper)

**Typography**:
- Font Family: Inter (body font)
- Font Size: text-base (16px)
- Font Weight: font-normal (400)
- Label: text-sm font-medium (14px, 500)
- Helper: text-sm (14px)
- Error: text-sm (14px)

**Colors**:
- Background: white/10 with backdrop-blur
- Border Default: white/20
- Border Hover: white/30
- Border Focus: blue-400
- Text: white
- Placeholder: white/50
- Error Border: red-400
- Error Text: red-400

---

### 10.8 Composition Breakdown

```
TextField Molecule
├── Label Atom (optional)
│   ├── Typography: text-sm font-medium
│   ├── Color: text-white/90
│   └── Required indicator (*) in blue-400
├── Input Container (relative positioning)
│   ├── Left Icon Atom (optional)
│   │   └── Position: absolute left-0
│   ├── Input Atom
│   │   ├── Background: white/10 + backdrop-blur-sm
│   │   ├── Border: white/20
│   │   ├── Typography: text-base
│   │   ├── Padding: px-4 py-3 (or pl-11/pr-11 with icons)
│   │   └── Border Radius: rounded-xl
│   └── Right Icon Atom (optional)
│       └── Position: absolute right-0
├── Error Message Atom (conditional)
│   ├── Color: text-red-400
│   ├── Typography: text-sm
│   └── Role: alert
└── Helper Text Atom (optional)
    ├── Color: text-white/60
    └── Typography: text-sm
```

---

### 10.9 Decision Tree

```
Which TextField variant should I use?

├─ Is this a standard form field?
│  └─ YES → variant="default" (DEFAULT)
│
├─ Do I have many fields in a dense form?
│  └─ YES → variant="filled" (subtler)
│
└─ Do I need to emphasize this field (e.g., search)?
   └─ YES → variant="outlined" (thicker border)
```

---

### 10.10 Anti-Patterns

❌ **Missing Label**
```tsx
// WRONG
<TextField name="email" placeholder="Email" />

// CORRECT
<TextField name="email" label="Email Address" placeholder="you@example.com" />
```

❌ **Using Placeholder as Label**
```tsx
// WRONG: Placeholder disappears on focus
<TextField name="pan" placeholder="PAN Number" />

// CORRECT: Label persists
<TextField name="pan" label="PAN Number" placeholder="ABCDE1234F" />
```

❌ **Not Showing Error Message**
```tsx
// WRONG: User doesn't know what's wrong
<TextField name="pan" error={true} />

// CORRECT: Clear error message
<TextField name="pan" error={true} errorMessage="Invalid PAN format" />
```

